section.our-products
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-12(data-aos="fade-right")
        h2.section-heading.section-heading--light
          | our Products

    .row.mt-3.mt-sm-5()
      .col-sm-4.col-md-5.mt-lg-5
        h2.section-heading--normal.text-uppercase(data-aos="fade-right")
          | HI-TECH BAtteries
        p.section-desc(data-aos="fade-right")
          | The raw materials for the production of HI-TECH batteries are subject to rigorous laboratory tests for checking conformity to standards. Further stringent tests are carried out at every stage of manufacture to ensure uniformity of process parameters.

      .col-sm-8.col-md-7
        .product-slider-wrapper(data-aos="fade-left")
          .swiper-container.products
            // Additional required wrapper
            .swiper-wrapper
              // Slides
              .swiper-slide
                .card.card--product
                  img.product-img(src="./img/product-img1.png" alt="product 1")
                  h2.product-title
                    | HI-TECH BAtteries
              .swiper-slide
                .card.card--product
                  img.product-img(src="./img/product-img2.png" alt="product 1")
                  h2.product-title
                    | HI-TECH BAtteries
              .swiper-slide
                .card.card--product
                  img.product-img(src="./img/product-img1.png" alt="product 1")
                  h2.product-title
                    | HI-TECH BAtteries
          // If we need pagination
          .swiper-pagination.product
          .products-link.text-right
            a(href="javascript:void(0);").link.link--small
              | view more
